onsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612041\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104azm1665702712331.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/azm1665702712331.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/azm1665702712331.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"azm1665702712331\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Direction\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Window property of a form that specifies the reading orientation of the form at runtime. If set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">right-to-left</code>, the layout and text orientation are mirrored.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"azm1665702712331__section_w4287ab1b5b1_w4288ab1b5_w4289ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__2\">\n Representation\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__2\">\n (Default)\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__3\">\n Use the value defined in the assignment file.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__2\">\n Right to Left\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__3\">\n Text is read from right to left. Use for right-to-left languages such as Hebrew and Arabic.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__1\">\n 2\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__2\">\n Left to Right\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"azm1665702712331__table_d11639e1_d11640e1_d11641e1__entry__3\">\n Text is read from left to right.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"azm1665702712331__section_qcl_35w_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d395803e123\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"azm1665702712331__p_d100022e1_d100023e1_d100024e1\">This property overrides the assignment setting\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$RTL_APPLICATION</span>, if it is present.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"azm1665702712331__p_d100025e1_d100026e1_d100027e1\">It is not possible to set this property in\n            ProcScript.</p>\n<div class=\"note tip note_tip\" id=\"azm1665702712331__note_fb1_m5w_swb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Tip:</span> If you want to set the direction of a specific\n            field, specify <code class=\"ph codeph\">RTL</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">LTR</code> code in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field\n               Layout</span>.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"azm1665702712331__p_d100028e1_d100029e1_d100030e1\">If <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Direction</span> is set to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">Right to Left</code>, this is applied even when running on a left-to-right\n            Windows system. Similarly, if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Direction</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">Left to\n               Right</code>, the form or field will read from left to right on a right-to-left\n            system.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"azm1665702712331__fig_ikh_45w_swb\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>LTR Form with Contained Form with Direction <code class=\"ph codeph\">Right to\n               Left</code></figcaption>\n<img alt=\"LTR form Right to Left\" class=\"image\" id=\"azm1665702712331__image_dsb_bvw_swb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/containedfrmrtl.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"azm1665702712331__section_zrp_2vw_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d395803e180\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"azm1665702712331__ul_bt5_fvw_swb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"azm1665702712331__li_d40451e1_d40452e1_d40453e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtm1665702721231.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$RTL_APPLICATION</a><p>Specify that the desktop application will read from right to left instead of from left to right. This causes the layout of all forms and their contents to be mirrored, so that the starting point for reading is the right side.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nvi1665702721301.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$RTL_FIELDS</a><p>Set the position of the cursor in the field at deployment. For right-to-left applications only.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iha1665702711837.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Field Layout Codes</a><p>Field layout codes specify how data is formatted for display. When multiple codes are specified, they must be separated by commas.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bch1665702773514.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$windowproperties</a><p>Set or return the current window properties of a Form instance.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612041\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612041\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Direction Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Direction Window property of a form that specifies the reading orientation of the form at runtime. If set to right-to-left , the layout and text orientation are mirrored. Value Representation Description 0 (Default) Use the value defined in the assignment file. 1 Right to Left Text is read from right to left. Use for right-to-left languages such as Hebrew and Arabic. 2 Left to Right Text is read from left to right. Description This property overrides the assignment setting $RTL_APPLICATION , if it is present. It is not possible to set this property in ProcScript. Tip: If you want to set the direction of a specific field, specify RTL or LTR code in the Field Layout . If Direction is set to Right to Left , this is applied even when running on a left-to-right Windows system. Similarly, if Direction is Left to Right , the form or field will read from left to right on a right-to-left system. Figure 1. LTR Form with Contained Form with Direction Right to Left Applies To Form Related Links $RTL_APPLICATION Specify that the desktop application will read from right to left instead of from left to right. This causes the layout of all forms and their contents to be mirrored, so that the starting point for reading is the right side. $RTL_FIELDS Set the position of the cursor in the field at deployment. For right-to-left applications only. Field Layout Codes Field layout codes specify how data is formatted for display. When multiple codes are specified, they must be separated by commas. $windowproperties Set or return the current window properties of a Form instance. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}